description: The team had feared the owners of the rings, inscribed with the names Ahmed and Doudou, were dead.
title: Europe migrant crisis: Rescuers find owners of wedding rings lost at sea
title_page: Europe migrant crisis: Rescuers find owners of wedding rings lost at sea - BBC News
maintext: "Ahmed was really emotional. He was happy to find the rings as they are something very personal. But he could not get from his mind the whole incident and the five people who had died."
